IMAPAccount outlook
Host outlook.office365.com
User tahirhbutt@outlook.com
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.outlookpass.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore outlook-remote
Account outlook

MaildirStore outlook-local
Path ~/.mail/outlook/
Inbox ~/.mail/outlook/Inbox

Channel outlook
Master :outlook-remote:
Slave :outlook-local:
Patterns * !* "INBOX" "Sent" "Drafts" "Archive" "Deleted"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

